data.description: Welcome to this stunning 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home nestled in a quiet cul-de-sac, offering a perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Two-story residence features trey ceilings in the bedrooms, enhancing the architectural charm and spacious feel. Abundant natural light floods the home, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The heart of the home is the kitchen, equipped with a center island and a bay breakfast area, ideal for morning gatherings. The sunken family room, complete with a cozy fireplace, provides a perfect space for relaxation, family time and gatherings. The covered front porch adds a welcoming touch to the home's beautiful exterior. The property includes a 2-car garage, offering ample storage and parking solutions. The home is just 5 to 8 minutes from I-77. This home is not just a residence but a retreat from the hustle and bustle of daily life. Don’t miss the opportunity to own this property. Schedule your visit today and come see your future home!
